            <div type="edition">
                <div type="textpart">
                    <ab>+ (S.) Die sabati qui erat nonus exxeunte mense aprilis. Presencia <rs
                            key="#Boni_viri/boni_homines">bonorum ominum</rs> corum nomina hic
                        subter leguntur, hi sunt <persName key="#Boni_viri/boni_homines #childOf"
                                ><name ref="Gherardus/f. Lanfranci">Girardus</name></persName>
                        <rs key="#childOf">filius</rs>
                        <persName key="#Judge #parentOf"><name ref="Lanfrancus/de Casale Alto/iudex"
                                >Lanfranci</name></persName>
                        <rs key="#Judge">iudicis</rs> de <placeName key="#Gastaldus/vicegastaldus"
                            ref="#places/2963">Casale Alto</placeName> et <rs key="#parentOf"
                            >pater</rs> eius Lanfrancus iudes et <persName
                            key="#Boni_viri/boni_homines #Gastaldus/vicegastaldus"
                            ref="#people/3764">Martinus</persName>
                        <rs key="#Gastaldus/vicegastaldus">gastaldio</rs> de Casale Alto. Ibique in
                        eorum presencia <persName
                            key="#Domus #childOf #siblingOf #Transactional_breve #Decima #Landed_possessions"
                                ><name ref="Ardicionus/f. Alberti">Ardicionus</name></persName>
                        filius <persName key="#parentOf"><name ref="Albertus/de Forminiano"
                                >Alberti</name></persName> de <placeName ref="#places/2964"
                            >Forminiano</placeName> et <persName
                            key="#childOf #siblingOf #Transactional_breve #Decima #Landed_possessions"
                                ><name ref="Albertus">Albertus</name></persName>
                        <rs key="#siblingOf">frater</rs> eius et <persName
                            key="#Transactional_breve #Decima #Landed_possessions"><name
                                ref="Teudaldus/de Adri">Tedaldus</name></persName> de <placeName
                            ref="#places/2965">Adri</placeName> per lignum quod in suhis manibus
                        tenebant fecerunt finem et transhaccionem <rs key="#Churches">heclesie</rs>
                        <orgName
                            key="#Churches #Monks #Missus #Transactional_breve #Decima #Landed_possessions"
                            ref="#juridical_persons/2001">Sancti Benedicti</orgName> per domnum
                            <persName key="#Monks #Missus #Transactional_breve" ref="#people/3765"
                            >Anselmum</persName>
                        <rs key="#Monks">monahcum</rs> et <rs key="#Missus">missum</rs> de <rs
                            key="#Decima">decimis</rs> de <rs key="#Landed_possessions"
                            >bragidis</rs> que fuerunt quondam <persName
                            key="#Count #Landed_possessions" ref="#people/2181">Uberti</persName>
                        <rs key="#Count">comitis</rs>. Penam insuper se obbligaverunt wiginti <rs
                            key="#Penalty">librarum denariorum bonorum Mediolanensium</rs> componere
                        siibsi per se aut per suos missos de decimis de bragidis adversus heclesiam
                        vel adversus successores eius agere aut causare presumsisent. Actum est hoc
                        loco Casale Alto, in <rs key="#Domus">domo</rs> Ardicionis feliciter. Anno
                        ab i[nca]rnacione domini nostri Hiesu Christi millesimo centesimo quinto,
                        mense aprilis, indicione terciadecima. Et ego <persName
                            key="#Writer #Transactional_breve #Judge #Notary" ref="#people/3763"
                            >Teuzo</persName> iudex et <rs key="#Notary">notarius</rs> rogatur hunc
                            <rs key="#Transactional_breve">brevem</rs> scribere <rs key="#Writer"
                            >scripsi</rs>. </ab>
